OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fmostly dry into Monday evening with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud giving a few
OL,8,Fclearer spells. A few showers or some
OL,9,Frain might return as cloud increases
OL,10,Fand thickens again later in the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FTurning breezier Tuesday,
OL,13,Fafter a cloudy morning with showery
OL,14,Frain. Rain dying out and clearing east
OL,15,Fin the afternoon with cloud breaking
OL,16,Fto allow some bright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
