OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday, morning rain clearing, then
OL,7,Fcolder, brighter and turning mostly
OL,8,Fdry. Thursday, windy and bright with
OL,9,Fthickening cloud later. Friday less
OL,10,Fwindy with sunshine and showers.
OL,11,FTemperatures near normal.
